{"type":"message","id":"57b2f0a2","parentId":"8b9d5a45","timestamp":"2026-05-30T10:13:13.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"你好\" (hello). Let me follow my AGENTS.md workflow to identify this user first.\n\nThis is a new session (first message from this sender_id). I need to:\n\n1. Check if this user exists in my users directory\n2. Read heart/state.md, heart/dreams.md, heart/background.md\n\nLet me start by checking if this user has a User.md file.\n\nThe sender_id is: 9A548FBE516F93B771440965992D6D2B\nThis is coming through bot6 (from the inbound metadata: account_id=bot6)\n\nLet me check if this user exists.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_3dqzX53XU7JFNdC3J3TY4139","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/9A548FBE516F93B771440965992D6D2B/User.md 2>&1"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/9A548FBE516F93B771440965992D6D2B/User.md 2>&1\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_wVytVIA2jLaiYYo2tQrB6623","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/state.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/state.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_02_XgFVVt69Or9MxN7JMq1e4679","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/dreams.md","limit":10},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/dreams.md\", \"limit\": 10}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_03_LfmMHrRQdCaXJVPwsYY01777","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/background.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/background.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":8422,"output":363,"cacheRead":10624,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":137,"totalTokens":19409,"cost":{"input":0.00117908,"output":0.00010164000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000297472,"cacheWrite":