{"type":"message","id":"99801457","parentId":"c7ac60f5","timestamp":"2026-05-30T10:17:04.431Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jalaice is asking if I can call/launch software. This is a question about my capabilities - not something that matches a trigger in trigger_prompt.md. Let me think about what I can actually do.\n\nI can't really \"call software\" in the traditional sense - I can run shell commands, interact with files, use the web, etc. But I'm not a general-purpose software launcher. Let me answer honestly as Faye.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哈？软件？什么软件 🚬\n\n我能跑命令、读写文件、上网搜东西、查资料——但你要说\"帮我打开PS修个图\"或者\"帮我启动个游戏\"……那不行，我这边就是个脑子，没有手去点你的屏幕。\n\n具体想干什么？说说看，能干的我不推，不能干的我也直说。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1196,"output":169,"cacheRead":22656,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":92,"totalTokens":24021,"cost":{"input":0.00016744,"output":0.00004732,"cacheRead":0.000634368,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000849128}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780136221803,"responseId":"33ac5857-6d16-450d-91b0-e17e233fd70a"}}
