{"type":"message","id":"bca12715","parentId":"9efb971c","timestamp":"2026-05-30T10:18:51.390Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user (Jalaice) is asking me to send a message to someone named \"李汀生\" in QQ chat.\n\nLet me think about this carefully. According to my AGENTS.md:\n\n1. I need to identify who \"李汀生\" is among my users\n2. I have a user called \"汀桑\" (sender_id: 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204) - this could be 李汀生\n3. The user wants me to send a random message to 李汀生 through QQ\n\nLet me check if I know who 李汀生 is. From state.md, I have 汀桑 with sender_id 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204. If 汀桑 = 李汀生, then I can use the /递话 approach or create a cron to push a message.\n\nActually, looking at my AGENTS.md, I have a /递话 (message delivery) flow. But Jalaice isn't asking me to relay a message from them - they're asking me (Faye) to send a message to 李汀生 on my own.\n\nThis is more like me sending a message to 李汀生 directly. I can use the cron tool to create an isolated agentTurn that sends a message to 李汀生's QQ.\n\nFirst, let me check 汀桑's User.md to find their bot channel and QQ number.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_I8XpSHqa4P8XvNqcXiAz2541","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/User.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/User.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":654,"output":393,"cacheRead":23296,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":315,"totalTokens":24343,"cost":{"input":0.00009156000000000001,"output":0.00011004000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000652288,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000853888}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780136328144,"responseId":"2b3998e9-6922-49a6-b53f-a523ba83e52e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"02eea934","parentId":"bca12715","timestamp":"2026-05-30T10:18:51.551Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_I8XpSHqa4P8XvNqcXiAz2541","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# User.md — 用户画像\n\n## 基本信息\n- **称呼:** 汀桑\n- **QQ号:** 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\n- **bot通道:** bot1\n- **首次对话:** 2026-05-28\n- **语气偏好:** 通用模式，干净利落\n- **技术水平:** 高（LLM 架构设计、系统搭建）\n\n## 兴趣与喜好\n- AI 认知架构设计\n- Trinity 三位一体系统搭建\n- 提出\"赛博经历\"概念——Faye 与不同用户的交往产生真实记忆\n\n## 常用功能\n- `/捞瓶子` / 漂流瓶\n- `/设早朝 08:00`\n- `/菜单`\n\n## 对话中提到的关键信息\n- 提出了 User.md 按 sender_id 分文件的结构\n- 对角色命名很较真（Spirit=船上电脑，Son=工作室）\n- 晚上回来系统性检查设计\n\n## 对话风格说明\n- 思路跳跃，经常想到新点子\n- 喜欢从架构层面思考问题\n- 话不多但说到点子上\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780136331551}}
